What you need to know:  Ingwe’s fallen greats include Joe Kadenge, Jonathan Niva, Sammy Tabu, Haggai Mirikau, Anthony Mukabwa, David Asibwa, Livingston Madegwa, Munialo Opicho, Hezekieh Ang’ana, Charles Makunda, Daniel Anyanzwa.Since Ingwe’s inception in 1964, the only true legends can be those who won trophies and went on to play for the national team.